# Package Map — Hana CMS Monorepo

> **Khi thêm/xoá package, plugin, hoặc app → cập nhật file này ngay.**

## Packages (`packages/`)

| Package | Npm scope | Mô tả | Được import bởi |
|---|---|---|---|
| `packages/types` | `@hana/types` | TypeScript interfaces/types ONLY — không có runtime logic | Tất cả packages, plugins, apps |
| `packages/validator` | `@hana/validator` | Zod schemas cho content, user, media, plugin | `@hana/core`, plugins, admin |
| `packages/schema` | `@hana/schema` | Drizzle base tables (`users`, `sessions`, `installed_plugins`), `mergeSchemas()` helper | `@hana/core`, plugins |
| `packages/core` | `@hana/core` | `HanaCMS` class, `HookRegistry`, `createDatabase()`, static admin serve | plugins, apps, CLI |
| `packages/registry` | `@hana/registry` | `PluginRegistryClient` — fetch plugin list, install/uninstall, verify SHA-256 integrity | `@hana/core`, `@hana/ui` |
| `packages/ui` | `@hana/ui` | Vue `ComponentRegistry`, base components, Plugin Marketplace UI | `apps/admin`, plugins |
| `packages/cli` | `@hana/cli` | CLI commands: `hanabi init`, `hanabi migrate`, `hanabi plugin install/uninstall` | standalone binary |
| `packages/config` | `@hana/config` | Shared tsconfig (`tsconfig.base.json`, `tsconfig.app.json`, `tsconfig.lib.json`) | Tất cả packages |

## Plugins (`plugins/`)

> Plugins là **Official plugins** — npm packages, cần `bun add` + restart.
> Khác với Community plugins (CDN bundle, dynamic import không cần restart).

| Plugin | Npm scope | Tính năng |
|---|---|---|
| `plugins/plugin-auth` | `@hana/plugin-auth` | Schema + routes cho authentication (đăng ký, đăng nhập, sessions) |
| `plugins/plugin-blog` | `@hana/plugin-blog` | Posts/categories schema + CRUD REST routes |
| `plugins/plugin-media` | `@hana/plugin-media` | File upload schema + routes (local storage adapter) |

## Apps (`apps/`)

| App | Filter name | Mô tả | Port mặc định |
|---|---|---|---|
| `apps/admin` | `@hana/admin` | Vue 3 SPA admin dashboard, build output embed vào `core/dist/admin` | 5173 (dev) |
| `apps/docs` | `@hana/docs` | VitePress documentation site | 5174 |
| `apps/starter` | `@hana/starter` | Template project cho end-users clone | — |

## Entry Points Quan Trọng

```
packages/core/src/hana-cms.ts       → HanaCMS class, createCMS()
packages/core/src/hook-registry.ts  → HookRegistry class
packages/core/src/database.ts       → createDatabase()
packages/types/src/plugin.ts        → CMSPlugin interface, CMSPluginHooks
packages/types/src/cms.ts           → CMSConfig, DatabaseConfig, AdminConfig
packages/schema/src/schema-builder.ts → mergeSchemas()
packages/registry/src/registry-client.ts → PluginRegistryClient
packages/registry/src/integrity.ts  → verifyBundle()
```

